room_title: Escape room "999 Strange Place" by Enter the Room in Colorado Springs
room_description:
Excited about your upcoming trip, you booked the perfect bed and breakfast for you and your group. Your worries are far gone as you pull up to your 5-star luxurious stay. You open the door, and to your dismay, things are far from what was advertised!
Trapped in the room, you slowly start to realize that you were lured to this house for a reason. Can you escape and enjoy your vacation, or will you join the owner of the house in his new form forever?
